metadata.description: Super Owl is a collection of 2,000 specially designed NFTs with the idea of making this project to help Orphans and 100% of the income will be given to Different Orphanages purely focusing on food and education. According to UNICEF (the United Nations Childrenâ€™s Emergency Fund), there are roughly 153 million orphans worldwide. Every day, an estimated 5,700 more children become orphans. Children are often relinquished due to war, natural disasters, poverty, disease, stigma, and medical needs. Let's Work together towards bringing smiles to the Kids' Face...
